features:
Hood with visor and wind seal around face with adjustable draw cord in back.
Waterproof YKK® front zipper with 3mm chain to minimize weight.
Waterproof flap behind zipper with garage.
Two front pockets with waterproof zips.
Back pocket with double slider on zip to enable use as stuff sack.
Chest strap with button to limit opening when jacket is unzipped.
Adjustable draw cord at bottom of jacket.
Adjustable Velcro at wrists.
Fit: Regular
Weight:180gr
